transcript:
Customer: Hello.
Executive: Haan boliye madam.
Customer: Haan ji Naveen Kumar ji se baat ho rahi hai meri?
Executive: Haan bataiye.
Executive: Hello sir, main Pallavi baat kar rahi hoon IndiaMART Noida head office se, E and Enterprise ke liye sir call kiya tha. Abhi sir aapka discussion hua tha aapke account manager Ashutosh ji se, main unhi ki manager baat kar rahi hoon sir. To sir jo bhi issues the sir abhi resolve ho gaye hain, koi cheez pending to nahi hai jo abhi aapko na clear ho?
Customer: Haan unhone sahi samjha diya, jab bhi koi dikkat hogi to main dobara poochh ke lunga, phone karke bata diya unhone mujhe.
Executive: Theek hai sir, bilkul number unhone apna share kar diya aap se?
Customer: Number to abhi koi number nahi diya unhone, bas isi se call kiya tha, NEET pe aake Google mein usi number pe baat kar.
Executive: Nahi nahi sir, main unse bol deti hoon, woh bhi aap se apna official number share kar denge. Further kuch bhi problem hoti hai to directly aap unse connect kar sakte hain, theek hai? Baki baki sir concern band karne ke baad ek feedback aayega aapke paas, jo bhi aapka unse discussion hua hai. To agar aap satisfied hain unke jo bhi discussion hua hai usse, aap please feedback zaroor positive share kar dijiyega sir, theek hai?
Customer: Ji ji.
Executive: Ji ji, okay okay, thank you sir, have a good day.
